OL,3,CUltramarathon champion dies while
OL,4,Crunning Highlands trail in honour of
OL,5,Cfriend
OL,7,FA former marine and ultramarathon
OL,8,Fchampion has died while taking on a
OL,9,Frunning challenge in the Highlands.
OL,11,FDavid Parrish, 35, was found dead on
OL,12,FSaturday at around 10.25pm in the
OL,13,FKintail region after mountain rescue
OL,14,Fteams launched a search to find him.
OL,16,FMr Parrish had taken on the 234-mile
OL,17,FCape Wrath Trail and was attempting to
OL,18,Fbeat the world record while running in
OL,19,Fhonour of a late friend.
