OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776276669
OL,3,CUltramarathon champion dies while
OL,4,Crunning Highlands trail in honour of
OL,5,Cfriend
OL,7,FHe was running the route to raise
OL,8,Fmoney in memory of Luke Ireland, who
OL,9,Fdied from hypothermia in November 2014
OL,10,Fwhile running in the Glen Clova
OL,11,Fmountains.
OL,13,FThe fundraiser, which has now passed
OL,14,Fthe #13,000 mark, will go towards
OL,15,FScottish Mountain Rescue (SMR), which
OL,16,Ffound and recovered Mr Ireland's body.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
