PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776276669
OL,3,CUltramarathon champion dies while
OL,4,Crunning Highlands trail in honour of
OL,5,Cfriend
OL,7,FMr Parrish had previously won the Cape
OL,8,FWrath ultramarathon in 2023.
OL,10,FVolunteers from Kintail Mountain
OL,11,FRescue Team (KMRT) led the search for
OL,12,FMr Parrish, eventually finding his
OL,13,Fbody.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for KMRT said: "Our
OL,16,Fthoughts are with David's family and
OL,17,Ffriends at this incredibly difficult
OL,18,Ftime.
