OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776276669
OL,3,CUltramarathon champion dies while
OL,4,Crunning Highlands trail in honour of
OL,5,Cfriend
OL,7,F"David was an experienced hillgoer and
OL,8,Fmountain runner who tragically died
OL,9,Fdoing something he loved."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for SMR said his loss
OL,12,Fwould be "felt sharply" and that
OL,13,Feveryone at the rescue service is
OL,14,F"devastated" by the news.
