OL,3,CUltramarathon champion dies while
OL,4,Crunning Highlands trail in honour of
OL,5,Cfriend
OL,7,F"David's dedication to honouring his
OL,8,Ffriend's memory, while raising funds
OL,9,Fto support our service, truly moved us
OL,10,Fall. His fundraising efforts will
OL,11,Fsupport our volunteer teams as they
OL,12,Fcontinue to respond to emergencies
OL,13,Facross Scotland's mountains, leaving a
OL,14,Flasting legacy to both friends in the
OL,15,FScottish outdoors."
OL,17,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,18,F"We were made aware of the death of a
OL,19,F35-year-old man found in the Kintail
OL,20,Farea around 10.25pm on Saturday April
OL,21,F11 2026.
